Class BaseOutputWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.jmxtrans.model.output.BaseOutputWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OutputWriter, OutputWriterFactory, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ElasticWriter, FileWriter, GangliaWriter, GraphiteWriter, KafkaWriter, KeyOutWriter, LibratoWriter, Log4JWriter, NagiosWriter, OpenTSDBGenericWriter, RRDToolWriter, RRDWriter, SensuWriter, Slf4JOutputWriter, StackdriverWriter, StatsDWriter, StdOutWriter.W, VelocityWriter

    @NotThreadSafe
public abstract class BaseOutputWriter
extends Object
implements OutputWriter, OutputWriterFactory
    Implements the common code for output filters. Note that the use of a non threadsafe @link{Map} makes this class non threadsafe.

    jon

      • getConcatedTypeNameValues

        protected String getConcatedTypeNameValues(String typeNameStr)
        Given a typeName string, get the first match from the typeNames setting. In other words, suppose you have:

        typeName=name=PS Eden Space,type=MemoryPool

        If you addTypeName("name"), then it'll retrieve 'PS Eden Space' from the string
